The '''emblem of the [[Commonwealth of Independent States]]''' ({{lang-ru|Флаг Содружества Независимых Государств}}) depicts a yellow sun on a dark blue field, with eight bending poles holding the sun. 

==Description==
[[File:Stamp 2011 CIS-20 (1).JPG|thumbnail|2011 stamp of [[Ukraine]]]]
The design (which reflects the one of the [[Flag of the Commonwealth of Independent States|flag of the Commonwealth]]) symbolizes the desire for equal partnership, unity, peace and stability.

