The '''Diocese of Monteverde''' (Latin: ''Dioecesis Montis Viridis'') was a Roman Catholic diocese located in the town of [[Monteverde]] in the [[province of Avellino]] in Southern Italy. In 1718, it was suppressed to the [[Roman Catholic Diocese of Sant' Angelo de' Lombardi-Bisaccia|Diocese of Sant'Angelo dei Lombardi e Bisaccia]].<ref name=CathHierMonteverde>[http://www.catholic-hierarchy.org/diocese/dm545.html "Diocese of Monteverde"] ''[[Catholic-Hierarchy.org]]''. David M. Cheney. Retrieved August 25, 2016</ref><ref name=GCathMonteverde>[http://www.gcatholic.org/dioceses/former/t1191.htm "Titular Episcopal See of Monteverde"] ''GCatholic.org''. Gabriel Chow. Retrieved August 25, 2016</ref>

